# Quality gates — Open Data Agro

> **Non-negotiable:** 0 ESLint errors, 0 ESLint warnings, tests green on changed packages.

## Before every PR or commit with code changes

Run from repo root (when toolchain exists):

```bash
pnpm lint              # ESLint — must exit 0, --max-warnings 0
pnpm typecheck         # TypeScript — all packages
pnpm test              # unit + integration tests
pnpm build             # all packages compile
```

Until scaffold exists, document manual verification in PR.

## Agent rules

- Do not claim `pnpm verify` passed without running it
- Fix lint/type errors in the same change — no follow-up commits for obvious failures
- New datasets require golden vectors from [docs/OFFICIAL-SOURCES.md](../docs/OFFICIAL-SOURCES.md)
